            <description><![CDATA[【夏天喜欢游泳友友看过来<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[打工人]" src="https://face.t.sinajs.cn/t4/appstyle/expression/ext/normal/a1/2023_earner_org.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E4%B8%A4%E6%8B%9B%E6%95%99%E4%BD%A0%E8%BE%A8%E5%88%AB%E6%B8%B8%E6%B3%B3%E6%B1%A0%E6%B0%B4%E8%B4%A8%23&amp;extparam=%23%E4%B8%A4%E6%8B%9B%E6%95%99%E4%BD%A0%E8%BE%A8%E5%88%AB%E6%B8%B8%E6%B3%B3%E6%B1%A0%E6%B0%B4%E8%B4%A8%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#两招教你辨别游泳池水质#</span></a>】夏季来临，很多小伙伴喜欢去游泳池觅凉解暑。问题来了，如何自测游泳池水质好坏？这两个方法速来get：①通过水面看水底泳道的情况，看得越远，说明清澈度越好；②把泳池里的水稍微打起水花，泡沫在10-15秒可以散开，说明水质较好👇🏻<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E5%94%A0%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%23&amp;extparam=%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E5%94%A0%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#小卫唠健康#</span></a>   <a href="https://video.weibo.com/show?fid=1034:4922743641014298" data-hide=""><span class="url-icon"><img style="width: 1rem;height: 1rem" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/upload/2015/09/25/3/timeline_card_small_video_default.png" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><span class="surl-text">央视频的微博视频</span></a><br clear="both"><div style="clear: both"></div><video controls="controls" poster="https://tvax3.sinaimg.cn/orj480/007S2YvRly1hfuaf9gp9uj31hc0u07jj.jpg" style="width: 100%"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/o0/5KO8leCYlx086X8zSo8w01041200tq6G0E010.mp4?label=mp4_720p&amp;template=1280x720.25.0&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=1CwnkDw1GXwCQx&amp;Expires=1689383054&amp;ssig=En6WRHGEtl&amp;KID=unistore,video"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/o0/m5NiU5rClx086X8zwy6Q01041200frdQ0E010.mp4?label=mp4_hd&amp;template=852x480.25.0&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=1CwnkDw1GXwCQx&amp;Expires=1689383054&amp;ssig=K4PNEPUpHP&amp;KID=unistore,video"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/o0/kuDLxnR9lx086X8z5kak010412009BFs0E010.mp4?label=mp4_ld